Package: RASCO
Type: Package
Title: An R Package to Alleviate Spatial Confounding
Version: 0.0.3
Author: Douglas R. M. Azevedo, Marcos O. Prates, Dipankar Bandyopadhyay
Maintainer: Douglas R. M. Azevedo <douglasrm.azevedo@gmail.com>
Description: Tools to implement several Bayesian restricted models to tackle spatial confounding in a variety of generalized linear mixed modeling, and survival analysis settings. 
